Package io.honeycomb.libhoney

Class TransportOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.honeycomb.libhoney.TransportOptions

  • public class TransportOptions
extends Object
    Holds configuration options for the transport layer HoneyClient, as well as their default values. These are advanced options to configure the internals, namely the batching operation, as well as the http client. For most applications the defaults will be good enough.
    See Also:
    DefaultBatcher, HoneycombBatchConsumer
